    bibo:volume "51" ;
    dc:creator "Marusik, Y. M.; Omelko, M. M." ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "A New Genus Of Tetragnathid Spiders From Papua New Guinea (Aranei, Tetragnathidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454193>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454195>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454197>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454191>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454203>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454199> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454193>
    dc:description "Figs 9–15. Somatic characters of Diphya macrophthalma (9–11), Nediphya lehtineni sp. n. (12–13) and N. hippai sp. n. (14–15)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6454193/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454195>
    dc:description "Figs 16–25. Male somatic characters of Nediphya lehtineni sp. n.: 16–17 — prosoma, frontal, and fronto-dorsal; 18 — metatarsus I showing stiff setae; 19, 21 — prosoma, ventral, both cheliceral claws broken; 20 — coxa IV, ventral; 22 — abdomen, ventral showing unmodified book lung operculae; 23 — spinnerets, caudal-ventral; 24 — tarsus II, showing pseudosegmentation (Ps); 25 — epiandrous fusules." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6454195/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454197>
    dc:description "Figs 26–33. Male palp of Nediphya lehtineni sp. n. (26–31) and Diphya macrophthalma (32–33): 26, 33 — retrolateral; 27 —ventral; 28 — dorsal; 29 —posterio-dorsal; 30, 32 — prolateral; 31 — anterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6454197/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454191>
    dc:description "Figs 1–8. Habitus of Nediphya lehtineni sp. n. (1–5), N. lyleae sp. n. (6), N. hippai sp. n. (7) and N. padillai sp. n. (8): 1 —male habitus, dorsal; 2, 6–8 — female habitus, dorsal; 3 — female prosoma, ventral; 4 — female prosoma, dorsal; 5 a, b — female leg I, a —dorsal and b —prolateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6454191/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454203>
    dc:description "Figs 52–54. Habitus of unknown Tetragnathidae female:" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6454203/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454199>
    dc:description "Figs 34–39. Male palp of Nediphya lehtineni sp. n.: 34–35 — whole palp, prolateral and retrolateral; 36 — anterio-ventral; 37 — anterio-dorsal; 38 — anterio-retrolateral; 39 — retrolateral. Abbreviations: Cf cymbial fold, Cl antero-retrolateral lobe of cymbium, Cm median tip of conductor, Co conductor, Cp prolateral tip of conductor, Cr retrolateral tip of conductor, Em embolus, Fc conductor furrow, Pd dorsal branch of paracymbium, Pl lateral branch of paracymbium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6454199/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

